## Notes for Future Development

### Multi-Ledger System (Phase 2)

The Source column is designed to eventually link to a multi-ledger account switcher system:

**Planned Features:**
- AccountManager class for managing up to 10 separate accounts
- Account switcher UI in header
- Transaction isolation per account (separate localStorage keys)
- Reconciliation drawer for cross-account reconciliation
- Source column becomes clickable to switch between accounts

**Current Implementation:**
- Source column shows prefix for visual reference
- Single-ledger system (all transactions in one store)
- No account switching capability yet

This will be implemented as a separate phase to maintain clean separation of concerns.

